      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It requires significant mechanical repairs as the engine is currently unreliable and the transmission slips. Cosmetically, there is heavy rust on the rocker panels and several large dents across the body. The interior is in rough shape with torn upholstery and a lingering odor, making this a suitable project car for someone with the tools and time to restore it.",
