      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m super excited to help this awesome car find its next home! It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really great shape, inside and out. It runs like a dream and is perfect for anyone who wants a dependable, stylish vehicle without paying those crazy dealership prices. I've taken good care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin!",
