    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders, with the dual-VANOS system recently serviced for optimal cam timing. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to address chassis fatigue, and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance. The suspension features upgraded polyurethane bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry remains communicative. While the Titanium Silver finish shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals are synchronized for spirited performance. A purist\u2019s spec with no sunroof for a lower center of gravity.",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
