    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered for sale is a beautifully maintained sedan that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated Midnight Onyx, which still holds a deep, mirror-like reflection. While there are a few minor touch-ups on the front bumper from standard road use, the body is remarkably straight with no significant dings or scratches. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free cabin appointed with supple pebble-grain leather. The heated power seats function flawlessly, and the dual-zone climate control keeps the interior perfectly tempered. Every button and switch, from the panoramic sunroof to the premium 12-speaker audio system, has been tested and works as intended. Mechanically, this car stands out with a fully documented service history at authorized centers. It has recently undergone a comprehensive 100-point inspection, receiving new brake pads and a fresh synthetic oil service. The tires have significant tread remaining, ensuring a smooth and quiet ride for many miles to come. This vehicle represents a well-cared-for example of its class, ready for its next owner with no immediate maintenance required.",
      "price": 32500.0,
